&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, log, and maintain gameplay issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct ad hoc and bug regression testing when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and execute test plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with execution of playtests including setup, moderation, participant handling, annotating, lab/equipment maintenance, and other research related activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide quality assurance and development support for our playtests.&lt;/li&gt;
